	* SpecCheck.py: Report all occurrences of egrep/fgrep on a line.
	* SpecCheck.py: Check for uses of deprecated egrep and fgrep
	  (https://bugzilla.redhat.com/571386).
	* SpecCheck.py: Recognize scriptlet section markers.

