	* BinariesCheck.py, Config.py, DistributionCheck.py, FilesCheck.py,
	  I18NCheck.py, InitScriptCheck.py, MenuCheck.py, MenuXDGCheck.py,
	  NamingPolicyCheck.py, PamCheck.py, Pkg.py, PostCheck.py,
