2008-10-29  Ville Skyttä <ville.skytta at iki.fi>

	* BinariesCheck.py, Config.py, ConfigCheck.py,
	  DistributionCheck.py, DocFilesCheck.py, FHSCheck.py,
	  FilesCheck.py, Filter.py, I18NCheck.py, InitScriptCheck.py,
