	  rpmlint.1, rpmlint.py: Use tempfile.gettempdir() instead of
	  hardcoding /tmp, Python >= 2.3 is now required.
	* README, rpmlint.1, rpmlint.py: Load all /etc/rpmlint/*config as
	  config files.

