	* PostCheck.py: Fine tune forbidden-selinux-command info message.
	* PostCheck.py: Check for forbidden SELinux related commands (Steve
	  Grubb, https://bugzilla.redhat.com/214605)
	* PostCheck.py: Drop some duplicate code.

